1. The spa is a place of relaxation and tranquility. Silence is requested. 2. It is mandatory to bring swimwear, appropriate footwear (flip flops for pool/spa use only) and a towel for personal use. We have flip flops for sale and towels for rent at the spa reception if necessary.
